  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“You must feel so much lighter now, clean and innocent as a maid on the morning of her wedding..” —Septa <a href=\"/index.php/Scolera\" title=\"Scolera\">Scolera</a><br /><i>I fucked <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime</a> on the morning of my wedding.</i> —<a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_54\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 54\">Chapter 54</a>, Cersei I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260406190716\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.006 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 59/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 318/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 524/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    3.879      1 -total\n100.00%    3.879      1 Template:Ref\n 59.70%    2.316      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26352-0!canonical and timestamp 20260406190716 and revision id 240613\n -->\n",
